magpie.models.regression

Class WekaRegression

  • java.lang.Object
    • magpie.models.BaseModel
      • magpie.models.regression.BaseRegression
        • magpie.models.regression.WekaRegression
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, WekaModel, AbstractRegressionModel, Citable, Commandable, Options, Printable, Savable

    public class WekaRegression
extends BaseRegression
implements WekaModel
    Implementation of WekaModel for regression purposes. To use this class, simply provide the name of the Weka algorithm and a list of options as input.

    Example: model = new models.classification.WekaClassifier trees.REPTree -L 5

    Usage: <Weka classifier> [<classifier options...>]
    Weka classifier: Name of a Weka classifier model (i.e. trees.REPTree). "?" to list options
    classifier options: Any options for that model. (see Weka Javadoc for these options)

    See Also:
